Five seconds. Four...

626
00:29:02.727 --> 00:29:05.395
Three... Two. Another quick breath.

627
00:29:13.771 --> 00:29:15.771
Excuse me. excuse me.
Gurney coming through.

628
00:29:15.773 --> 00:29:18.441
It's okay. it's okay. it's
okay. it's okay. it's okay.

629
00:29:18.443 --> 00:29:20.488
- Gurney coming through.
