You're okay. You're all right.

696
00:32:03.941 --> 00:32:05.107
You're okay. Yeah. okay.

697
00:32:05.109 --> 00:32:07.277
Oh. God. my leg. Ow!

698
00:32:07.280 --> 00:32:09.444
Mickey?

699
00:32:09.447 --> 00:32:11.013
What the... oh. God.

700
00:32:11.015 --> 00:32:12.081
What the hell is going...?

701
