easy on a woman scorned.

756
00:34:26.882 --> 00:34:28.883
but not on one who hurts a cop.

757
00:34:30.488 --> 00:34:33.088
So untie me. I can help you.

758
00:34:33.090 --> 00:34:35.799
but you have to untie me.

759
